        "authorId" : "a3f1fdb0-47ad-411e-b63d-af6fc71a1fa6",
        "body" : "Actually when `setuptools` is in play, I have had a lot of trouble if I don't define these here. Otherwise `setuptools` makes entrypoints that require `pkg_resources`. Adding them here ensures `conda-build` creates the entrypoints so `setuptools` can't mess them up.\n",
